data.description: Presenting a spacious and meticulously maintained two-family residence, offering an ideal living arrangement in a desirable neighborhood. The main level features three well-appointed bedrooms, a comfortable living room, a fully-equipped kitchen, and a modern bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find an expansive second floor with four generously sized bedrooms, another inviting living area, an additional well-designed kitchen, and a contemporary bathroom. Completing this impressive property is a fully finished basement, providing extra space for various needs. Commuting is a breeze, as it's conveniently located near the 2 and 5 train station, with an express bus service to Manhattan and the Q21 Bus.. The vibrant Morris Park Ave is also just a stone's throw away. With its excellent condition and move-in readiness, this residence offers an exceptional opportunity for those seeking comfort, convenience, and space.
